OL,3,CTeen with Down Syndrome on a mission
OL,4,Cto tidy up town and raise money for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Rob
OL,8,FSmith reports on a young man turning
OL,9,Ftrash into cash, despite facing health
OL,10,Fchallenges
OL,12,FA teenager living with Down Syndrome
OL,13,Fhas been on a mission to tidy up his
OL,14,Fhometown and raise money for charity
OL,15,Fin the process.
OL,17,FTheo Avraam has been filling bags with
OL,18,Frubbish from across Northwich in
OL,19,FCheshire since October 2025 in an
OL,20,Feffort to clean up his home town and
OL,21,Fraise money for Down Syndrome Cheshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
