OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773493903
OL,3,CTeen with Down Syndrome on a mission
OL,4,Cto tidy up town and raise money for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FThe charity supports people of all
OL,8,Fages with Down Syndrome and their
OL,9,Ffamilies from across Cheshire,
OL,10,Fincluding 19-year-old Theo.
OL,12,FBut when he learned Down Syndrome
OL,13,FCheshire needs to raise #40,000 by
OL,14,Fsummer 2026 to keep its hub open, he
OL,15,Ftook it upon himself to take on a
OL,16,Flitter picking challenge to raise
OL,17,Fmoney for the charity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
