FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773493903
OL,3,CTeen with Down Syndrome on a mission
OL,4,Cto tidy up town and raise money for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FSo far, Theo has raised more than
OL,8,F#1,900 for the charity despite having
OL,9,Fto postpone a number of his
OL,10,Flitterpicks for multiple open-heart
OL,11,Fsurgeries.
OL,13,FHe's had repeated procedures since he
OL,14,Fwas a child.
OL,16,FTheo's mum Helen was on the litter
OL,17,Fpick we joined with him near Chester,
OL,18,Fshe said: "It gave us a focus, so we
OL,19,Fcould think not about the surgery but
OL,20,Fthe number of bags we're going to
OL,21,Fcollect.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
