OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773493903
OL,3,CTeen with Down Syndrome on a mission
OL,4,Cto tidy up town and raise money for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FTheo admits he's still in some pain
OL,8,Fafter his latest surgery but he's
OL,9,Fdetermined to reach his target.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
